dcterms:description: A FAQ dataset consisting of 72 FAQs regarding the credit card application process, prepared to answer user queries regarding general card information, pre-application issues, and post-application services.
dcterms:title: FAQ dataset regarding the credit card application process

dcterms:description: A dataset of 30 in-domain and Out-of-Domain (OOD) queries, containing English and Hinglish queries for evaluating the performance of the embedding model.
dcterms:title: Dataset of 30 in-domain and OOD queries

dcterms:description: A dataset created for training the embedding model using ChatGPT and small manual tagging, consisting of approximately 3.5k queries for training, 1k for validation, and 1014 for testing.
dcterms:title: Dataset for training the embedding using ChatGPT and small manual tagging

dcterms:description: A dataset of 1733 (state, action, rating) tuples created during the training of a policy model for optimizing the RAG pipeline.
dcterms:title: Dataset of 1733 (state, action, rating) tuples
